        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 3. — Phlyctocythere sicula n. sp.: A, holotype (MNHN PMC.O8H.1.10.2012) right valve, external lateral view;B, I, paratype (MNHN PMC.O28P.1.10.2012);C, D, F-H paratype (MNHN PMC.O29P.1.10.2012); B, left valve,external lateral view;C, left valve,internal view; D, left valve, internal view, muscle scars; E, left valve, dorsal view, drawing of outline; F, left valve, internal view, detail of the central part of the hinge; G, left valve, internal view, detail of the anterior part of the hinge; H, left valve, internal view, detail of the posterior part of the hinge; I, left valve, detail of ornamentation in ventral area. Scale bars: A-C, E, 200 µm; D, 100 µm; F-H, 50 µm; I, 20 µm." ;
